*                                                             *
*                 NSA CMOS3 STANDARD LIBRARY                  *
*                                                             *
* Contains cells from the NSA CMOS3 cell library. This        *
* library is mainly interesting in that full layouts on the   *
* cells are availible, as is complete process specifications. *
* The cells are named after the cell numbers of the original, *
* as "G0000". The "G" is for "government", and the four       *
* digits following are the original cell number.              *
*                                                             *
**************************************************************}
